#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.argpartition.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.argpartition"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:1 of
msgid ""
"Perform an indirect partition along the given axis using the algorithm "
"specified by the `kind` keyword. It returns an array of indices of the "
"same shape as `a` that index data along the given axis in partitioned "
"order."
msgstr ""
"使用 `kind` 关键字指定的算法沿给定轴执行间接分区。它返回一个与 `a` 形状"
"相同的索引数组，该数组沿给定轴以分区顺序索引数据。"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:8 of
msgid "Tensor to sort."
msgstr "要排序的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:10 of
msgid ""
"Element index to partition by. The k-th element will be in its final "
"sorted position and all smaller elements will be moved before it and all "
"larger elements behind it. The order all elements in the partitions is "
"undefined. If provided with a sequence of k-th it will partition all of "
"them into their sorted position at once."
msgstr ""
"用于分区的元素索引。第 k 个元素将位于其最终排序位置，所有较小的元素将被"
"移到它之前，所有较大的元素将被移到它之后。分区中所有元素的顺序是未定义的"
"。如果提供了一个 k-th 序列，它将一次性将所有元素分区到其排序位置。"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:17 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which to sort. The default is -1 (the last axis). If None, the"
" flattened tensor is used."
msgstr "用于排序的轴。默认值为 -1（最后一个轴）。如果为 None，则使用展平的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:20 of
msgid "Selection algorithm. Default is 'introselect'"
msgstr "选择算法。默认为 'introselect'"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:22 of
msgid ""
"When `a` is a tensor with fields defined, this argument specifies which "
"fields to compare first, second, etc. A single field can be specified as "
"a string, and not all fields need be specified, but unspecified fields "
"will still be used, in the order in which they come up in the dtype, to "
"break ties."
msgstr ""
"当 `a` 是具有定义字段的张量时，此参数指定首先、其次等比较哪些字段。单个字"
"段可以指定为字符串，并非所有字段都需要指定，但未指定的字段仍将在 dtype 中"
"出现的顺序用于打破平局。"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:29 of
msgid ""
"**index_tensor** -- Tensor of indices that partition `a` along the "
"specified axis. If `a` is one-dimensional, ``a[index_tensor]`` yields a "
"partitioned `a`. More generally, ``np.take_along_axis(a, index_tensor, "
"axis=a)`` always yields the partitioned `a`, irrespective of "
"dimensionality."
msgstr ""
"**index_tensor** -- 沿指定轴对 `a` 进行分区的索引张量。如果 `a` 是一维的"
"，则 ``a[index_tensor]`` 产生分区后的 `a`。更一般地，``np.take_along_axis"
"(a, index_tensor, axis=a)`` 总是产生分区后的 `a`，无论维度如何。"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:37 of
msgid ":py:obj:`partition`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:38 of
msgid "Describes partition algorithms used."
msgstr "描述所使用的分区算法。"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:40 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Tensor.partition`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:41 of
msgid "Inplace partition."
msgstr "就地分区。"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:43 of
msgid ":py:obj:`argsort`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:44 of
msgid "Full indirect sort"
msgstr "完全间接排序"

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:47 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.sort.argpartition.argpartition:48 of
msgid "See `partition` for notes on the different selection algorithms."
msgstr "有关不同选择算法的说明，请参见 `partition`。"

